    "en": {
      "title": "A fuel report is requested from the Supreme Court",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Supreme Court ordered the Attorney General today (04) to clarify which areas are given priority in fuel purchase, distribution and fuel distribution and file a related report to the court before the 12th.",
        "The three-member Supreme Court bench consisting of Mr. Vijith Malalgoda, Mr. Mahinda Samayawardena and Mr. Arjuna Obeysekera issued this order when two fundamental rights petitions presented by the Sri Lanka Bar Association were reconvened today (04).",
        "These facts were presented when two fundamental rights petitions filed by the Sri Lanka Bar Association were called today (04) requesting the government to issue an order to prepare long-term and short-term solutions to the current economic crisis in the country."
      ],
